    {
      "actionDate": "2026-06-03",
      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p>This resolution provides for the House of Representatives to consider&nbsp;on the same day without a two-thirds vote&nbsp;any resolution reported by the Committee on Rules through the legislative day of June 5, 2026, relating to a measure providing for reconciliation pursuant to title II of S.Con.Res.33. Specifically, the resolution waives a House Rule requiring a two-thirds vote to consider a report from the Committee on Rules on the same day it is presented to the House.</p>",
      "updateDate": "2026-06-05T14:17:14Z",
